ActElectoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
SubjectProclamation Establishing Electoral Boundaries Commissions
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue establishing the electoral boundaries commissions and that each commission consist of the persons who are appointed as provided in sections 5 and 6 of the Electoral Boundaries Readjustment Act .
